706710f-a.title: Brooklyn: Sheepshead Bay Road - 15th Street (East)
706710f-a.text:
Sheepshead Bay Road, at the N.W. corner of East 15th Street, showing the Adelphi Hotel owned by Casper Schuessler in 1891.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
